## UiSystem-A2 搜索与过滤架构
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 草案
**标签：** stack:frontend

```typescript
function filterTree(tree: GoalsTree, query: string): GoalsTree {
  const q = query.toLowerCase()
  
  function filterNode(node: GoalNode): GoalNode | null {
    // Check if node matches
    const selfMatch = 
      node.id.toLowerCase().includes(q) ||
      node.title.toLowerCase().includes(q) ||
      node.tags.some(t => 
        `${t.kind}:${t.value}`.toLowerCase().includes(q)
      )
    
    // Filter children
    const filteredChildren = node.children
      .map(filterNode)
      .filter((n): n is GoalNode => n !== null)
    
    // Include node if self matches OR has matching descendants
    if (selfMatch || filteredChildren.length > 0) {
      return {
        ...node,
        children: filteredChildren,
        expanded: true,  // Auto-expand if matches
      }
    }
    
    return null
  }
  
  return {
    roots: tree.roots
      .map(filterNode)
      .filter((n): n is GoalNode => n !== null),
  }
}
```

| 查询 | 匹配项 |
|---|---|
| `Specs-G7` | Goal ID Specs-G7 |
| `wiki` | Title or tag value contains "wiki" |
| `module:wiki` | Tag with kind=module, value=wiki |
| `team:ui` | Tag with kind=team, value=ui |

- 搜索速度快（在预加载的树结构上进行客户端过滤）
- 每次按键无需服务器往返
- 自动展开确保用户看到所有匹配项

